Annie Ewart (born 29 September 1993) is a Canadian former racing cyclist. She rode at the 2014 UCI Road World Championships.
Major results
;2013
: 4th Time trial, Pan American Road Championships
;2014
: 8th Chrono Gatineau
;2015
